		<title>Rooting the Seagate GoFlex Home!</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.openstora.com/component/content/article/56-rooting-the-seagate-goflex-home"/>
		<published>2010-10-18T11:06:09Z</published>
		<updated>2010-10-18T11:06:09Z</updated>
		<id>http://www.openstora.com/component/content/article/56-rooting-the-seagate-goflex-home</id>
		<author>
			<name>pippone</name>
		<email>neothematrix@libero.it</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;thanks to a user &quot;3354h3hj&quot; who reported it, it is also possible for Seagate GoFlex Home users to gain root access to their device, this opens up a lot of possibilities to customize it (i.e. adding stuff like transmission server, amule, iSCSI, NFS, and more!) and to know more about the device you have by accessing every aspect of it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The procedure to get the root access is the same as the Netgear Stora, using a particular ssh user as explained on this wiki page: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.openstora.com/wiki/index.php?title=Easy_Root_Access&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;there is a note explaining the only different step, which is the different username.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enjoy and don't forget to post something on the new dedicated forum section!&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;thanks to a user &quot;3354h3hj&quot; who reported it, it is also possible for Seagate GoFlex Home users to gain root access to their device, this opens up a lot of possibilities to customize it (i.e. adding stuff like transmission server, amule, iSCSI, NFS, and more!) and to know more about the device you have by accessing every aspect of it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The procedure to get the root access is the same as the Netgear Stora, using a particular ssh user as explained on this wiki page: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.openstora.com/wiki/index.php?title=Easy_Root_Access&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;there is a note explaining the only different step, which is the different username.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enjoy and don't forget to post something on the new dedicated forum section!&lt;/p&gt;</content>
